         <abstract>
            <p>It is shown that the initial-value problem of the question (tu&lt;sub&gt;t&lt;/sub&gt;)&lt;sub&gt;t&lt;/sub&gt; = u&lt;sub&gt;xx&lt;/sub&gt; with the value of u prescribed for t = 0 has a unique solution satisfying a maximum principle. In addition, several numerical schemes for its solution are proposed.</p>
          </abstract>
